STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Romulo GREGORIO, Defendant-Petitioner. C-173 September Term 2018
080925 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 05, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003690-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
